content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 137.4 - Garage rates

State Regulations

The rates for storing automobiles, irrespective of the
geographical location of the institution, are fixed at $1 per month for a
shelter; $2 for an unheated garage; and $3 for a heated
garage. Notes
